<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Profile Approved</title>
</head>

<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
    <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 5px;">
        <div
            style="background-color: #4CAF50; color: white; text-align: center; padding: 10px; border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;">
            <h1>Profile Approved</h1>
        </div>
        <div style="padding: 20px 0;">
            <p>We are pleased to inform you that your profile for our MedicalHub platform has been approved by our admin
                team.</p>
            <p>Your profile is now live and visible to patients on our platform. You can start accepting appointments
                and providing consultations.</p>
            <p>If you need to make any changes to your profile or have any questions, please don't hesitate to contact
                our support team.</p>
            <p>
                <a href="<%= loginURL %>"
                    style="display: inline-block; padding: 10px 20px; background-color: #4CAF50; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px;">Login
                    to Your Account</a>
            </p>
            <p>Thank you for being a part of our MedicalHub network. We look forward to your valuable contributions in
                providing healthcare services to our patients.</p>
            <p>Best regards,<br>MedicalHub Team</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>